Components & Design
1. Main Controller
Siemens S7-1200 PLC
Model: CPU 1212C AC/DC/Relay (6ES7212-1HE40-0XB0)
8 DI, 6 DO, expandable
Reliable for industrial environment
Expansion for Stepper/Servo Control (PTO Outputs)
Siemens Signal Board SB 1231 (if you need extra AI)
Siemens Pulse-train module not required → CPU1212C already supports PTO up to 100 kH

2. Servo Motors + Drivers (for PPP axes)

Payload 5 kg + 1 m horizontal travel requires servo motors, not steppers.
X Axis (1 m travel)
Servo motor: Delta ECMA-C20807RS (750 W, 3000 rpm)
Driver: Delta ASDA-B2 series (Model: ASD-B2-0721-B)
Transmission: HTD 5M belt, 25 mm wide OR ballscrew SFU1610
Y Axis (1 m travel)
Servo motor: Delta ECMA-C20604RS (400 W)
Driver: Delta ASD-B2-0421-B (400 W driver)
Transmission: HTD 5M belt, 20–25 mm width
Z Axis (0.8–1 m vertical travel)
Servo motor: Delta ECMA-C20807RS (750 W)
Driver: Delta ASD-B2-0721-B
Transmission: Ballscrew SFU1610 with BK/BF supports + linear guides

3. Linear Motion Components (Mechanical, but essential electrically)
Linear Guides
Hiwin HGR20 rails (20 mm width)
Blocks: HGW20CC (4 per axis)
Ballscrews
SFU1610 (16 mm dia, 10 mm pitch) for Z
SFU1605 or HTD 5M belt drive for X & Y

4. Sensors for Material Classification
Metal Detection
Inductive sensor: LJ12A3-4-Z/BX
Type: PNP Normally Open
Voltage: 10–30 VDC

Plastic vs Paper Detection
Capacitive sensor: LJC18A3-B-Z/BX
Type: PNP Normally Open
Voltage: 10–30 VDC

Weight Measurement
Load cell: 5 kg aluminum plate load cell
Industrial amplifier: Waveshare Load Cell Amplifier 0–10 V output
Output directly to PLC analog input (AI0)

5. Gripper (Pneumatic)
Parallel Pneumatic Gripper
SMC MHZ2-20D
Solenoid Valve
SMC SY3120-5LZD-01
Voltage: 24 VDC
3-way, single solenoid
Pneumatic Air Preparation
SMC AF20-N02 (filter)
SMC AR20-N02 (regulator)

6. Power Supply System
For PLC, sensors, valves (24 VDC bus)
Meanwell LRS-350-24
24 V
14.6 A
For servo drives (48 VDC bus)
Meanwell RSP-750-48
48 V
60 A
For load cell amplifier
Same 24 V bus (it accepts 12–24 V)




7. Safety Components
Main Breaker
Schneider GV2-ME10 (adjustable 6–10 A)

Emergency Stop
Schneider XALK178 mushroom E-stop

Fuses
5×20 mm fuse holders
3A fuse for 24V logic
10–15A fuse for servo power input
Surge & Noise Protection
Ferrite cores on all servo cables
EMI filter: Schaffner FN2070-10-06

8. Cables & Wiring
Servo Motor Power Cables
4-core shielded, 2.5 mm² (for 750 W)
4-core shielded, 1.5 mm² (for 400 W)
Length: Typically 8–10 m per axis


Encoder/Signal Cables
6-core shielded twisted pair
0.5–0.75 mm²
10 m per axis

Sensor Cables
3-wire shielded, 0.5 mm²
5–10 m
PLC Wiring
Single core 0.75 mm² for DO/DI
1.0	mm² for 24V distribution

9. Electrical Enclosure Components
Metal enclosure 600×400×200 mm (steel)
DIN rails (2× 350 mm)
Cable ducts
24VDC terminal blocks (Weidmüller)
Grounding bar
Cooling fan 120mm + filter
